Validation of invoice no. syntax before entering into the database 
- No. must be consistent with the syntax "COUNT_NUM / MONTH / YEAR"
- COUNT_NUM - any positive integer consisting of any number of digits 
- MONTH - a number between 1-12 (digits only). Numbers 1-9 are preceded by a "0" sign on the left side.
- YEAR - any positive integer consisting of 4 digits